=============================================================================

Phase-Tuned-Feathering: peer-review / publication .gitignore

Repository: https://github.com/pwimero/Phase-Tuned-Feathering

Goal:

Keep the reproducible RCAA / feathered-wingtip code, benchmarks, scripts,

documentation, selected validation outputs, and manuscript-facing files public.

Exclude local editor settings, caches, raw heavy outputs, private notes,

credentials, and temporary run artifacts.

=============================================================================

